      "description": "This vehicle is in extraordinary, mint condition, presenting as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless with a deep luster, free of any chips, scratches, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, featuring pristine upholstery and a clean, factory-fresh scent. Every mechanical and electronic system functions perfectly, and the car has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. A truly exceptional example for a discerning buyer.",
